<?xml version="1.0" encoding="ASCII"?>
<caldef:CalDefinitionFile xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:caldef="http://www.caltools.gm.com/caldef" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.caltools.gm.com/caldef caldef_1.0.xsd">
  <CalDefFileVersion>12</CalDefFileVersion>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>2</Version>
    <Date>2/24/2015</Date>
    <Description>This speech caldef was last included in cal database release version 0.6, but it shouldn't have been removed and is needed for MY17. So it's being readded.</Description>
    <Author>Xufang Zhao</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>3</Version>
    <Date>10/30/2015</Date>
    <Description>Updated Integer Array values in integer array for CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_US_ENGLISH CAL. Renamed FSG_END_OF_UTTERANCE_TIMEOUT CAL to END_OF_UTTERANCE_TIMEOUT. Deleted the NL_EOU_TIMEOUT CAL, ONE_SHOT_DESTINATION_LEADING_SILICENCE CAL, ONE_SHOT_DESTINATION_TRAILING_SILENCE CAL, SPEECH_MANUAL_INTERACTION_TIMEOUT CAL, and VOICE_KEYPAD_CONT_DIGITS_TIMEOUT_EXTENDED CAL. Deleted the previous CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_FRENCH_CANADIAN CAL (CALID: _ypujFE1AEeO3UM5MzM17kw) because the incorrect ArrayLenghth of  60 was defined for this CAL. Adding a new CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_FRENCH_CANADIAN CAL (CALID: _Vl8bcH8hEeWf199FS_W2qg) to define with the correct array length of 120. Also, added the following new CALs that have been confirmed to be needed: 1.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_MEXICO_SPANISH CAL, 2.) MEXICANSPANISH_PHONE_NUMBER_GROUPING_PLAYBACK_PAUSE_LENGTH, 3.) CANADIANFRENCH_PHONE_NUMBER_GROUPING_PLAYBACK_PAUSE_LENGTH, and 4.) USEnglish_PHONE_NUMBER_GROUPING_PLAYBACK_PAUSE_LENGTH.</Description>
    <Author>Xufang Zhao</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>4</Version>
    <Date>12/1/2015</Date>
    <Description>Based on feedback received from Jideok Son, made usage correction to remove Low Radio usage for all of the calibrations within this CalDef file.</Description>
    <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>6</Version>
    <Date>5/27/2016</Date>
    <Description>Removed server credential string arrays for each language (SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_ITALIAN, SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_EUSPANISH, SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_UKENGLISH, SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_EUFRENCH,SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_GERMAN, SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_MANDARIN, SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_MEXICANSPANISH, SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_CANADIANFRENCH, and SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_USENGLISH). Added three new calibrations (SPEECH_REC_SERVER_CREDENTIAL_NA_Region, SPEECH_REC_SERVER_CREDENTIAL_EU_Region, and SPEECH_REC_SERVER_CREDENTIAL_CH_Region) as credential JSon files for NA, European, and Chinese regions. Added a new calibration, ASR_Engine_PARAM, to calibrate speech recognition engine parameters. </Description>
    <Author>Xufang Zhao</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>5</Version>
    <Date>3/7/2016</Date>
    <Description>Changed the name of the following 3 CALs 1.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_MEXICO_SPANISH to EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_MEXICANSPANISH, 2.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_FRENCH_CANADIAN to EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_CANADIANFRENCH, and 3.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_US_ENGLISH to EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_USENGLISH. The new CAL names include the word EMBEDDED at the beginning of the CAL name to make it easier to distinguish between the embedded and new server speech recognition CALs being added within this caldef file for MY18. Also, updated the some of the default values within the following calibration arrays: EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_MEXICANSPANISH, EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_CANADIANFRENCH, and EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_USENGLISH. Also, within this caldef file added the following 33 new MY18 ASR related calibrations: 1.) HighConfidenceShortcut, 2.) SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_MEXICANSPANISH, 3.) SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_CANADIANFRENCH, 4.) SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_EUFRENCH, 5.) SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_GERMAN, 6.) SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_ITALIAN, 7.) SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_EUSPANISH, 8.) SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_MANDARIN, 9.) SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_UKENGLISH, 10.) SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_USENGLISH, 11.) EnableServerASR_Global, 12.) EnableServerASR_USENGLISH, 13.) EnableServerASR_CANADIANFRENCH, 14.) EnableServerASR_MEXICANSPANISH, 15.) EnableServerASR_MANDARIN, 16.) EnableServerASR_GERMAN, 17.) EnableServerASR_EUFRENCH, 18.) EnableServerASR_UKENGLISH, 19.) EnableServerASR_EUSPANISH, 20.) EnableServerASR_ITALIAN, 21.) TsEmbededTimeOut, 22.) TsServerTimeOut, 23.) SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_ITALIAN. 24.) SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_EUSPANISH, 25.) SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_UKENGLISH, 26.) SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_EUFRENCH, 27.) SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_GERMAN, 28.) SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_MANDARIN, 29.) SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_MEXICANSPANISH, 30.) SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_CANADIANFRENCH, 31.) SPEECH_REC_SERVER_QUERRYPARAMS_USENGLISH, 32.) TTS_Voice_Level,and  33.) Listening_BEEP_Level. Also added the following 15 new Array type CALs (1.) EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_ARABIC, 2.) EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_DANISH,3.)  EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_DUTCH, 4.)  EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_EUFRENCH, 5.) EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_GERMAN, 6.) EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_ITALIAN, 7.) EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_KOREAN, 8.) EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_POLISH, 9.) EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_EUPORTUGUESE, 10.)EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_RUSSIAN , 11.)  EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_EUSPANISH, 12.) EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_MANDARIN, 13.) EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_TURKISH, 14.) EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_UKENGLISH, and 15.) EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_AUSENGLISH to define these CALs with the correct Array Lenght of 120 needed for this CALs. And deleted, the following 15 assoicated Array Type CALs that had the incorect length of 60 defined: 1.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_ARABIC, 2.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_DANISH, 3.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_DUTCH, 4.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_FRENCH, 5.)CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_GERMAN, 6.)CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_ITALIAN, 7.)CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_KOREAN, 8.)CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_POLISH, 9.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_PORTUGUESE,10.)CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_RUSSIAN,11.)CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_SPANISH, 12.)CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_STANDARD_CHINESE, 13.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_TURKISH, 14.)CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_UK_ENGLISH, and  15.)CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_AUSTRALIAN_ENGLISH. Also, deleted the following 24 calibrations confirmed no longer to be needed: 1.) MEXICANSPANISH_PHONE_NUMBER_GROUPING_PLAYBACK_PAUSE_LENGTH, 2.) CANADIANFRENCH_PHONE_NUMBER_GROUPING_PLAYBACK_PAUSE_LENGTH, 3.) USEnglish_PHONE_NUMBER_GROUPING_PLAYBACK_PAUSE_LENGTH, 4.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_BRAZILIAN_PORTUGUESE, 5.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_BULGARIAN, 6.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_CROATIAN, 7.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_CZECH, 8.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_GREEK, 9.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_HUNGARIAN, 10.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_JAPANESE, 11.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_LATIN_SPANISH, 12.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_NORWEGIAN, 12.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_ROMANIAN, 13.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_SLOVAK, 14.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_SLOVENIAN, 15.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_SWEDISH, 16.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_THAI, 17.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_TRAD_CHINESE, 18.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_UKRAINIAN, 19.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_SOUTH_AFRICA_ENGLISH, 20.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_STANDARD_CHINESE_CANTONESE, 21.) CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_TRAD_CHINESE_CANTONESE, 22.) ONE_SHOT_DESTINATION_MAXIMUM_USER_SPEECH_TIME, 23.) REGIONAL_PHONE_NUMBER_GROUPING_PLAYBACK_PAUSE_LENGTH, and 24.) VOICE_KEYPAD_CONT_DIGITS_TIMEOUT.</Description>
    <Author>Xufang Zhao</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>7</Version>
    <Date>Inital release of this CAL.</Date>
    <Description>Within the SpeechRecognitionPerformance.caldef file for RTC CR#: 1228981, added the following two new calibration parameters for new MY19 speech features.EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_BRAZPORTUGUESE and HighConfidenceShortcut_Server</Description>
    <Author>Xufang Zhao</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>8</Version>
    <Date>6/15/2017</Date>
    <Description>Updated the usage field for all of the calibration to support the new &quot;Global A/B&quot; categorization in the CalDef tool.</Description>
    <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>9</Version>
    <Date>5/11/2018</Date>
    <Description>Move server HCT/LCT values from MY19/MY20 CAL override to MY21 default; Move embedded US English HCT/LCT values from MY19/MY20 CAL override to MY21 default</Description>
    <Author>Xufang</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>10</Version>
    <Date>5/11/2018</Date>
    <Description>Per CR# 1743709, changed the default value to true for the EnableServerASR_MEXICANSPANISH and EnableServerASR_CANADIANFRENCH calibrations within the SpeechRecognitionPerformance.caldef file. Also, per CR# 1743709 changed the default value to match the caloverride values released in MY19 within the following calibrations SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_MEXICANSPANISH, SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_CANADIANFRENCH, SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_EUFRENCH, SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_GERMAN, SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_ITALIAN, SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_EUSPANISH, SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_MANDARIN, SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_UKENGLISH, EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_USENGLISH, SERVER_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_USENGLISH, EnableServerASR_UKENGLISH, and EnableServerASR_GERMAN, and updated the updated default value for two index values (6 and 7) within the EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_USENGLISH array.</Description>
    <Author>Xufang Zhao</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>11</Version>
    <Date>27MAR2019</Date>
    <Description>Added 'ENTRY_VCU' and 'VCU' tags for initial creation of VCS compatible CalDefDatabase for version GIS-646 V6.0.0 release.</Description>
    <Author>Scott Rush</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>12</Version>
    <Date>4/23/2020</Date>
    <Description>Within SpeechRecognitionPerformance.caldef file per agreement with Calibration Software PO (Jason Litchfield) and others on the software team, the SOURCECHANGETIMEOUT cal is being removed becasue there were duplicate instances of this cal found within the CalDB. It is also being removed because no one on the infotainment requirements team could identify any requirements linked to this calibration. We believe this cal to have been a legacy cal going back to at least the NGI variant radio that got carried over, and never should have been included in the CalDB for Info3.x.</Description>
    <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefinition Description="Confidence threshold settings for LCT (Low Confidence Threshold), HCT (High Confidence Threshold), and CSD (Confidence Score Delta) for embedded speech recognition. There shall be multiple pairs of configurable thresholds used to classify the results. Each domain based SLM shall have its own threshold pair. The combined SLM used at the highest level of the user interface shall have its own pair of thresholds. Additionally there shall be a threshold for critical commands. This critical command threshold shall be configurable for commands whose action it deemed to be difficult to reverse thus the system shall be more cautious about acting on it." Name="EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_BRAZPORTUGUESE" References="GIS-381" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
