    <CalID>_Vl8bcH8hEeWf199FS_W2qg</CalID>
    <Type>IntegerArray</Type>
    <Version>2</Version>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>1</Version>
      <Date>10/30/2015</Date>
      <Description>Deleted the previous CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_FRENCH_CANADIAN CAL (CALID: _ypujFE1AEeO3UM5MzM17kw) because the incorrect ArrayLenghth of  60 was defined for this CAL. Adding a new CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_FRENCH_CANADIAN CAL (CALID: _Vl8bcH8hEeWf199FS_W2qg) to define with the correct array length of 120.</Description>
      <Author>Xufang Zhao</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>2</Version>
      <Date>3/7/2016</Date>
      <Description>Changed the name of this CAL from CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_FRENCH_CANADIAN to EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_CANADIANFRENCH to also include the word EMBEDDED at the beginning of the CAL name to make it easier to distinquish between the embedded and new server speech recognition CALs being added within this caldef file for MY18.  Also, updated some of the default values within this calibration array.</Description>
      <Author>Xufang Zhao</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
