  <CalDefinition Description="There shall be multiple pairs of configurable thresholds used to classify the results. Each domain based SLM shall have its own threshold pair. The combined SLM used at the highest level of the user interface shall have its own pair of thresholds. Additionally  there shall be a threshold for critical commands. This critical command threshold shall be configurable for commands whose action it deemed to be difficult to reverse  thus  the system shall be more cautious about acting on it." Name="EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_ARRAY_DUTCH" References="GIS-696" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
