  <CalDefinition Description="There shall be multiple pairs of configurable thresholds&#xA;used to classify the results. Each domain based SLM&#xA;shall have its own threshold pair. The combined SLM&#xA;used at the highest level of the user interface shall have&#xA;its own pair of thresholds.&#xA;Additionally  there shall be a threshold for critical&#xA;commands. This critical command threshold shall be&#xA;configurable for commands whose action it deemed to&#xA;be difficult to reverse  thus  the system shall be more&#xA;cautious about acting on it." Name="EMBEDDED_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD_USENGLISH" References="GIS-696" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
    <CalID>_yp130k1AEeO3UM5MzM17kw</CalID>
    <Type>IntegerArray</Type>
    <Version>4</Version>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>1</Version>
